        "description": "CFD solver must be under formal version control with documented release testing; all simulation scripts traceable to a tagged repository commit; regression test suite covering ≥90% of relevant solver modules must pass; independent code review of user-defined functions (UDFs) for hemolysis model required."
      },
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R2 is used under FDA CDRH's formal SQA framework. Version control is maintained via Git with tagged releases. All UDFs implementing the Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power-law are independently reviewed and regression-tested against the ASME V&V 20 benchmark suite. Achieved Gradation 4: documented SQA plan, version-controlled solver, independent UDF review, and regression test pass rate of 97.3%."
