      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental data (Hariharan et al. 2011) provides fully documented boundary conditions with calibrated instrumentation (±1.5% flow rate, ±0.5 mmHg pressure). MIH measurements performed per ASTM F1841 with bovine blood at 37°C, hematocrit 40±2%. Pump geometry dimensionally verified via CMM against FDA CAD: maximum deviation 0.07 mm. Achieved Gradation 4: fully documented experimental conditions with traceable uncertainty budgets and geometry verification."
