      "rationale": "All momentum, continuity, and turbulence residuals drop 5+ orders of magnitude within 2000 iterations per time step. Mass imbalance: 0.004% of inlet mass flow. Hemolysis scalar residual reaches 8×10⁻¹³ at each time step — below machine precision threshold. Double-precision arithmetic used throughout. Achieved Gradation 4: documented iterative convergence with residual plots archived, mass balance verified, and scalar transport converged to machine precision."
