        "description": "All material properties (blood density, viscosity) must be traceable to ASTM or ISO standards or peer-reviewed sources with documented uncertainty. Geometric inputs must be traceable to FDA-verified CAD with dimensional verification. Boundary conditions must be traceable to calibrated experimental measurements with documented uncertainty budgets."
